  <h2>1. Delivery</h2>
  <p>All products sold on this site are digital and delivered electronically. Once your payment is confirmed, your files are sent to the email address you provided at checkout, typically within a few minutes. If you do not receive your files within 24 hours, contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:eliza_1990@abv.bg">eliza_1990@abv.bg</a>.</p>

  <h2>2. Refund window</h2>
  <p>You may request a full refund within <strong>14 days</strong> of purchase, provided the digital content has not been downloaded or accessed. Once a file has been downloaded, the statutory EU withdrawal right for digital content ends, and refunds are then granted at our discretion — for example where a product is defective, materially not as described, or undeliverable due to a technical fault on our side.</p>

  <h2>3. How to request a refund</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Email <a href="mailto:eliza_1990@abv.bg">eliza_1990@abv.bg</a> with your order confirmation and the reason for your request.</li>
    <li>We aim to respond within one business day and, where a refund is approved, process it within 5–10 business days to your original payment method.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Exchanges</h2>
  <p>If you purchased the wrong product, contact us before requesting a refund — in most cases we can simply swap it for the correct one at no extra cost.</p>

